FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Got questions about our food delivery service? We've got answers!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the food delivery app work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app connects you with local restaurants and delivers food straight to your door. Simply browse menus, place your order, and track your delivery in real-time.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Delivery fees vary based on distance and restaurant. The exact fee will be displayed before you complete your order. We also offer a subscription service for free delivery on eligible orders.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How long does delivery usually take?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Delivery times typically range from 30-45 minutes, depending on the restaurant's preparation time and delivery distance. You can always check the estimated delivery time before placing your order.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I schedule an order for later?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! Our app allows you to schedule orders up to a week in advance. Simply select your desired delivery time during checkout.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What if there's an issue with my order?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: If you experience any problems with your order, please use the 'Help' section in the app to report the issue. Our customer support team is available 24/7 to assist you and ensure your satisfaction.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the food delivery process work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app connects you with local restaurants. Simply browse menus, place your order, and track your delivery in real-time. Our drivers will bring your food right to your doorstep.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Delivery fees vary based on your distance from the restaurant and order size. You can view the exact fee before confirming your order. We also offer a subscription service for free delivery on eligible orders.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How can I track my order?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Once your order is confirmed, you can track its status in real-time through our app. You'll receive updates when the restaurant starts preparing your food, when the driver picks it up, and when they're approaching your location.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: What if there's an issue with my order?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: We're committed to your satisfaction. If there's any problem with your order, please use the 'Help' section in our app to report the issue. Our customer service team will assist you promptly with refunds or redeliveries as needed.
